                          "value": {
                            "type": "constant", 
                            "value": "<b>Relative Size</b>: We use the size of an object to tell us about distance. If you are looking at a stand of trees, you expect the trees that are closer to you to appear larger and the trees farther away to appear smaller. <br /><br /><br /><br /><br /><br /><br />"
