                        {
                          "name": "caption", 
                          "value": {
                            "type": "constant", 
                            "value": "<b>Overlap</b>: If an object is covering up or partially blocking another object, we assume it\u2019s closer. Alternatively, the object being blocked is assumed to be farther away. For example, in this photo, you can tell that the fourth pin from the right is in front of the third pin from the right."
